    "actor_description": "It hits like a lift under the ribs-too bright to hold neatly. My chest feels wide, my skin lightly charged, thoughts sprinting ahead of my mouth. I want to move, to speak, to share the fact of being alive right now. Even my laughter feels involuntary, like my body is leaking sunlight.",
